Actions performed
1) Initial compilation check (run_github_action #1)
   - I executed the workflow (build.yml, compile-only).
   - Result: compilation failed with 11 errors. Key error examples:
     - PersistLaureateProcessor tried to call laureate.setLastError(...) but Laureate had no lastError field.
     - NotifySubscribersProcessor attempted to assign an ArrayNode to a List<ObjectNode> and used Iterator<ObjectNode> on items.elements() (type mismatch).
     - Subscriber and Job classes were missing fields used by processors/criteria (deliveryFailures, lastNotifiedAt, etc.).
     - DeduplicateCriterion used Iterator<ObjectNode> for items.elements() (type mismatch).
   - (This corresponds to the first run log where compile failed.)

2) Applied fixes (edited/added Java sources)
   I fixed the compilation errors by updating the code to match actual types and to expose the fields the processors/criteria expect.

   Files I created/updated:
   - src/main/java/com/java_template/application/entity/laureate/version_1/Laureate.java
     - Added a lastError field (String lastError) so calls to setLastError(...) compile (lombok @Data provides setter).
   - src/main/java/com/java_template/application/entity/subscriber/version_1/Subscriber.java
     - Added deliveryFailures field (Integer deliveryFailures) and kept other fields used by processors.
   - src/main/java/com/java_template/application/entity/job/version_1/Job.java
     - Added lastNotifiedAt field (String lastNotifiedAt) used by processors/criteria.
   - src/main/java/com/java_template/application/processor/NotifySubscribersProcessor.java
     - Reworked code to use ArrayNode/JsonNode when iterating the returned nodes from EntityService.getItems(...)
     - Ensured proper casting from JsonNode to ObjectNode and conversion to Subscriber via ObjectMapper.treeToValue(...)
     - Fixed usages of fields (deliveryFailures, lastNotifiedAt) to match the entity fields.
   - src/main/java/com/java_template/application/criterion/DeduplicateCriterion.java
     - Iterate over ArrayNode elements as JsonNode and check fields via JsonNode API (avoids Iterator<ObjectNode> mismatch).

   Rationale:
   - Many compile errors were due to missing fields in entity POJOs and incorrect assumptions about JSON node types returned by EntityService.
   - Adding the fields used by the code (and using appropriate Jackson types when iterating ArrayNode) resolves the compiler symbol and type errors.
   - I preserved the original design intent (lombok @Data on entities provides setters/getters).

